title: #317 'TOXIC MASCULINITY' DEBUNKED! Dennis Prager and Gavin McInnes Guest
description: Talking all things David Hogg’s upcoming book, Amy Schumer’s new movie, cat rapist, Spiderman pedophiles, Time’s 100 list, and more. We’ll also be debunking the idea of “toxic masculinity” and ruining Seven Brides for Seven Brothers. Dennis Prager and Gavin McInnes stop by for the usual shenanigans.
